rom the center of Babylon to the heart of Huntington Station. It encompasses neighborhoods in Deer Park, Dix Hills, Elwood, East Northport, Greenlawn and Melville, and a diversity of race, religion and wealth. Still, there are common issues - concerns that affect working families like yours and mine. As a member of the Suffolk County Legislature, I promise to be part of a government based on strong vision, positive action and determined leadership. Together, we will work to find solutions to make our community better and provide our children with the same opportunities and quality of life that we enjoy.</p> <p>Again, thank you for your support and confidence. I look forward to serving as your representative.</p><p>Sincerely,</p><img src="images/stern_signature.jpg" with="200" height="61" alt="Stern signature" /><p>Steven Stern, County Legislator-Elect</p></div><div id="bottom"><a href="about/">About Steve</a> | <a href="16thdistrict/">About the District</a> | <a href="media/">Media</a> | <a href="issues/">Issues</a> | <a href="events/">Events Schedule</a> | <a href="volunteer/">Volunteer</a> | <a href="contribute/">Contribute</a> | <a href="contact/">Contact</a> | <a href="./">Home</a><p>&copy; 2005 Friends of Steve Stern. This site has been validated for <a href="http://validator.w3.org/check?uri=http://www.stevestern2005.us">XTHML 1.0</a> and <a href="http://jigsaw.w3.org/css-validator/validator?uri=http://www.stevestern2005.us/basic.css">CSS 2.0</a> by the <a href="http://www.w3.org">World Wide Web Consortium.</a></p></div></div></body></html>